snippet.title: Salt 1 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Set sail with friends or alone across an infinite world filled with pirates, treasure, quests, epic loot, and countless islands! Fight captains, build a ship, hunt and fish for food, and take on epic adventures in the world of Salt.
